Algorithm: Single Inheritance
Step 1:Define a parent class family with a method relation.
Step 2:Define a child class relatives that inherits from family.
Step 3:Create an instance r of the relatives class.
Step 4:Call the inherited method relation() and the class's own method relation1().

Code: Single Inheritance
class family:
    def relation(self):
        print("This is Family")

class relatives(family):
    def relation1(self):
        print("This is Relatives")

r = relatives()
r.relation()
r.relation1()

Output: Single Inheritance
This is Family
This is Relatives


Algorithm: Multiple Inheritance
Step 1:Define two independent classes: Writer and Speaker.
Step 2:Define class Author that inherits from both Writer and Speaker.
Step 3:The Author object a now has access to methods from all three classes.
Step 4:Execute methods sequentially to take user input and display it.

Code: Multiple Inheritance
class Writer:
    def write(self):
        self.write_name = input("Enter writer name: ")
        print(self.write_name)

class Speaker:
    def speak(self):
        self.speak_name = input("Enter speaker name: ")
        print(self.speak_name)

class Author(Writer, Speaker):
    def role(self):
        self.author_name = input("Enter author name: ")
        print(self.author_name)

a = Author()
a.write()
a.speak()
a.role()

Output: Multiple Inheritance
Enter writer name: Navratan
Navratan
Enter speaker name: Sanjay
Sanjay
Enter author name: Prakash
Prakash

ALGORITHM: MULTILEVEL INHERITANCE
Step 1:Create a base class School.
Step 2:Create a derived class Student that inherits from School.
Step 3:Create a further derived class Monitor that inherits from Student.
Step 4:The Monitor object inherits the entire chain of attributes and methods.

CODE: MULTILEVEL INHERITANCE
class School:
    def school_name(self):
        print("ABC School")

class Student(School):
    def student_name(self):
        print("Student of the School")

class Monitor(Student):
    def duty(self):
        print("Monitor of the class")

m = Monitor()
m.school_name()
m.student_name()
m.duty()

OUTPUT: MULTILEVEL INHERITANCE
ABC School
Student of the School
Monitor of the class

